WEBVTT

00:01.293 --> 00:03.295
- Just let it go?
- No.

00:03.378 --> 00:06.340
Why wouldn't
l wanna go to the symphony?

00:06.423 --> 00:09.593
- l didn't mean anything by it.
- You meant something.

00:09.676 --> 00:12.638
- We've got to do something.
- No, we really don't.

00:12.721 --> 00:15.724
Carla's your girlfriend,
Elliot's my friend...

00:15.807 --> 00:18.060
Trust me. Don't get involved.

00:18.143 --> 00:20.938
<i>She's from el barrio,
she must not like music.</i>

00:21.021 --> 00:25.817
- Classical music isn't for everyone.
- So, l didn't have a nanny...

00:28.278 --> 00:30.405
You got something to say?

00:31.240 --> 00:35.786
l think you're being condescending
and you're being overly sensitive.

00:42.251 --> 00:45.128
Excuse me for a second,
just one second.

00:47.000 --> 00:53.074
